text: A Millionaire for Christy is a 1951 American comedy movie directed by George Marshall and starring Fred MacMurray, Eleanor Parker, Richard Carlson, Una Merkel, Douglass Dumbrille. It was distributed by 20th Century Fox. ==Other websites== * * * Category:1951 comedy movies Category:American comedy movies Category:Movies directed by George Marshall
title: A Millionaire for Christy
